In mysql:

  1. Create database 'aruba'
  2. Create db user 'mvc' with password 'mvc'
  3. Run /migration script(s) to populate db with test values

Make sure the following directories are writable by apache:
	/public/css
	/public/js
	/log

Tail /log/mvc.log to check for installation errors

Apache .conf:
	<Directory /www/mvc >
			Options FollowSymLinks
			AllowOverride All
			Order deny,allow
			Deny from None
	</Directory>

	<VirtualHost *:80>
			ServerAdmin jarek707@gmail.com
			DocumentRoot "/www/mvc"
			ServerName mvc 
			ServerAlias mvc 
			SetEnv SERVER_ENV local
			ErrorLog "/private/var/log/apache2/mvc-error_log"
			CustomLog "/private/var/log/apache2/mvc-access_log" common
	</VirtualHost>
